<br>
1.) the way i use, earth pet, ds'd and then hit /pet get lost right before you have the next earth casted.  repeat (solo'ed in ME at 54)<br>
<br>
2.) deferred chaining, regular one pet fighting, but then reclaiming after the fight and then summoning a new pet.  <br>
<br>
3.) this is the one i am curious about, people have talked about reclaming pets in battle and resummoning.  This is the one i am curious about because it seems to be the potentially most mana efficient.  <br>
<br>
